    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174470/extras/d771983e56d8960a6243df76c660832a.avif?t=1770675758\" width=616 height=127 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A world shattered, a mission failed. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As a Pyramid Guard, your duty was to prevent this catastrophe.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Now, you awaken to a realm corrupted by Blight; a soul-sucking, spectral energy unleashed by an invading cybernetic Legion. With your kingdom shattered, your only hope lies in recovering the Totem keys: artifacts with the mystical power to banish the Blight - and keep it entombed for eternity.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But you won't face this challenge alone. The fate of your fellow Pyramid Guards is unknown - and some still roam these ravaged lands, united in their quest to banish the Blight for good.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174470/extras/26195e4a21b632a3120bf6e38638ec0f.poster.avif?t=1770675758\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174470/extras/26195e4a21b632a3120bf6e38638ec0f.webm?t=1770675758\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174470/extras/26195e4a21b632a3120bf6e38638ec0f.mp4?t=1770675758\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174470/extras/011d7fd451c0d4c1dfb11b563e430a4d.avif?t=1770675758\" width=616 height=127 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Frenetic and varied first-person combat reminiscent of genre classics </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 20 weapons to fight back the forces of the Legion </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collectible Aura points, which can be exchanged for weapon upgrades </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A plethora of power-ups and abilities for surviving in style. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A never-before seen Techno-Egyptian setting </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hordes of super-charged foes to give you a challenge </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Secrets galore!</p></li></ul>",
